    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable commuter for many years. The exterior shows its age with various minor scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small scuff on the front bumper. Inside, the upholstery has noticeable wear and a few permanent stains, though all essential controls and electronics are still operational. Mechanically, it starts reliably and drives fine, though it may eventually require some routine maintenance to address minor leaks typical of its age. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone needing affordable transportation.",
